message.raw:
Spinor lab changes to BIAS calc/fitting behaviour.
"Fit function" now a parameter from script used to choose python script.
Compute "Fit" has parameter "fit clip" and "bin size" uses geometric mean of array size, parameter names to match.
Pixel size taken into account for "fit_num"
Changed name of zlock server to zlock.physics
Name change on "Compute OD" to say Isat, etc
